<h4><a href="https://www.gizmodo.com.au/2020/11/top-vfx-company-attempts-to-bridge-uncanny-valley-fails/">数字王国发布「仿真实时自主数字人类」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381176" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-8.gif" alt="" width="648" height="357" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-8.gif 648w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-8-360x198.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ Doug Roble 在 Zoom 会议中对话「Douglas」</p>
</div>
<p>曾为《泰坦尼克号》《复仇者联盟：无限战争》等影片打造出色特技效果的数字王国，近日发布了名为「Douglas」的「仿真实时自主数字人类」。</p>
<p>「Douglas」的外貌和仪态基于数字王国软件研发高级总监 Doug Roble，但这个样貌并不是固定的，只要输入某人的特定数量视频素材，Douglas 就可以「变脸」。</p>
<p>Douglas 明年将作为「个性化」和「仿真」的虚拟助手和聊天机器人解决方案推出市场。</p>
<h4><a href="https://pocketnow.com/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-3-might-launch-sooner-than-expected?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+pocketnow+%28pocketnow.com%29">Galaxy Z Fold 3 或于明年 6 月发布</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381177" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/noet.jpg" alt="" width="751" height="418" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/noet.jpg 751w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/noet-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px" /></p>
<p>Pocketnow 援引韩媒体《亚洲日报》消息称，三星或将于明年 6 月发布 Galaxy Z Fold 3，搭载第二代 UTG 超薄玻璃，更薄且抗折痕能力更强；并将支持 S Pen。</p>
<p>此前就有传言称，三星将以折叠屏产品取代 Galaxy Note 系列。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.wallpaper.com/technology/airbird-chipring-smart-sensor">建筑师设计了一款「金丝雀」空气检测器</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381178" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/airbird-horizonal-low.jpg" alt="" width="1680" height="1120" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/airbird-horizonal-low.jpg 1680w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/airbird-horizonal-low-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/airbird-horizonal-low-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/airbird-horizonal-low-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px" /></p>
<p>丹麦建筑事务所 3XN 联手数据分析公司 Leapcraft 研发设计了一款「室内气候检测器」AirBird，适用于家庭、办公室和教室等空间。</p>
<p>AirBird 内置的传感器可实时检测空气中的二氧化碳水平。当空气中的二氧化碳浓度过高时，AirBird 就会发出鸣叫声，以提醒用户是时候开窗通风了。</p>
<p>其设计灵感源自「矿井中的金丝雀」。因为金丝雀对瓦斯的敏感度远高于人类，所以煤矿工人过去会将金丝雀带到矿井中用作「报警鸟」。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://techcrunch.com/2020/11/23/snapchat-launches-a-tiktok-like-feed-called-spotlight-kick-started-by-paying-creators/">Snapchat 推出类 TikTok 视频信息流功能 Spotlight</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381179" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Triptych_Product.jpg" alt="" width="990" height="556" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Triptych_Product.jpg 990w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Triptych_Product-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Triptych_Product-768x431.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px" /></p>
<p>TechCrunch 消息，Snapchat 在应用中上线了类似 TikTok 的短视频信息流功能 Spotlight，用户可不断下滑屏幕观看短视频。Snaps 宣称其算法将为各个用户定制推荐内容。</p>
<p>为了鼓励用户在 Spotlight 创造和发布内容，Snap 将每天拿出超过一百万美元奖励（16 岁或以上）创作者，激励机制将持续至 2020 年底。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5309901.html">苹果首席安全官被指控向警察行贿</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381186" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/RickJensenSJI.jpg" alt="" width="772" height="350" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/RickJensenSJI.jpg 772w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/RickJensenSJI-360x163.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/RickJensenSJI-768x348.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ Thomas Moyer 和 Rick Sung</p>
</div>
<p>新浪消息，周一公布的起诉书显示，加利福尼亚州地方检察官指控苹果公司首席安全官 Thomas Moyer 向该州官员行贿。Thomas Moyer 代理律师辩称其无罪。</p>
<p>圣克拉拉县警长 Rick Sung 涉嫌故意为苹果公司的安全团队扣留了四张美国隐蔽持枪许可证。Thomas Moyer 则承诺，苹果将向该警长办公室赠送 200 台 iPad，价值 7.5 万美元。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.cn/tech/2020-11-23/detail-iiznezxs3313702.d.html?mon=$mon">Gartner：Q3 全球智能手机出货下滑 5.7%</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381180" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Fold-2-review.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Fold-2-review.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Fold-2-review-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Fold-2-review-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Fold-2-review-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>新浪科技消息，Gartner 新报告指出，今年第三季度全球智能手机出货量为 3.66 亿部，同比下滑 5.7%。分析人士称，Q3 出货量仍有下滑，但与今年上半年相比有了明显的改善。</p>
<p>品牌方面，Q3 三星出货量为 8082 万部，市场份额为 22%；华为为 5183 万部，市场份额为 14.4%；小米为 4441 万部，市场份额为 12.1%；苹果为 4060 万部，市场份额为 11.1%。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.ifeng.com/c/81de7ijkjrq">网络直播新规公布：直播打赏实行实名制，设置最高限额</a></h4>
<p>《21 世纪经济报道》消息，国家广播电视总局发布关于加强网络秀场直播和电商直播管理的通知。《通知》规定，将对直播打赏实行实名制管理，限制未成年人打赏，设置打赏限额和打赏金额提醒等，还要禁止主播通过雇佣水军等方式鼓动、怂恿用户打赏。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2020/11/16/national/hokkaido-monster-wolf-wild-bears/">为了赶走野熊，日本支起了「机械狼」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381181" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/np_file_51312.jpeg" alt="" width="2000" height="1472" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/np_file_51312.jpeg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/np_file_51312-360x265.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/np_file_51312-768x565.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/np_file_51312-1024x754.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>《日本时报》消息，日本泷川市为了驱赶野熊，安装了两只「机械狼」。</p>
<p>当「机械狼」检测到动态时，它的眼睛会发出红光，并发出警告声（可模仿狼嚎、猎人的声音、枪声等 60 种不同声音）。声音的多样性可避免野熊习惯警告声。</p>
<p>近月来，日本各地报告的野熊目击次数达到了五年来最高。自 4 月起，政府收到了 1.3 万次报告。</p>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/AxW_mA1UXXDKdl5it2AfOQ">钟薛高母公司推出水饺品牌</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381182" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/jiaozi.jpg" alt="" width="718" height="384" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/jiaozi.jpg 718w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/jiaozi-360x193.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 718px) 100vw, 718px" /></p>
<p>FBIF 消息，钟薛高母公司推出水饺品牌「理象国」，其产品已经上线天猫旗舰店。</p>
<p>该品牌的水饺和钟薛高的冰淇淋一样，定位为「高端」，每枚水饺均价为 3 元左右，口味包括黑猪肉白菜、黑猪肉三鲜、干贝韭菜和鸡丝松茸四种。</p>
<h4><a href="http://news.mtime.com/2020/11/23/1604828.html">《流浪地球》加长版发布定档海报</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1381183" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/095029.84414106_620X620.jpg" alt="" width="620" height="868" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/095029.84414106_620X620.jpg 620w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/095029.84414106_620X620-360x504.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></p>
<p>时光网消息，《流浪地球》加长版《流浪地球：飞跃 2020 特别版》发布定档海报，官宣 11 月 26 日重映。</p>
<p>和原版相比，重映版增加了 11 分钟 44 秒 2 帧的内容。本次影片发行为惠民放映，票价不高于 15 元。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%AF%95%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%9F%E4%BB%8E%E4%BA%8B%E5%85%BB%E8%80%81%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%A5%966%E4%B8%87%23&amp;Refer=top">北京毕业生从事养老服务最高奖 6 万</a></h4>
<p>据《北京市养老服务人才培养培训实施办法》，北京设立应届毕业生入职奖励：本科及以上 6 万元、专科（高职）5 万元、中职 4 万元的标准，分三年发放入职奖励，鼓励引导高素质人才到养老服务行业入职从业。</p>
<p>网友：「有点心动。」「现在的年轻人应该都不会靠孩子养老了，有条件的都会自己做养老打算。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357580" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed.png" alt="" width="1029" height="165" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-360x58.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-768x123.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1024x164.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>歌荒？来试试奥巴马的歌单吧</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380770" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Em-fk7rW8AQPfEZ.jpeg" alt="" width="1024" height="512" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Em-fk7rW8AQPfEZ.jpeg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Em-fk7rW8AQPfEZ-360x180.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Em-fk7rW8AQPfEZ-768x384.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>随着新传记发售，奥巴马在 Twitter 上分享了一份汇集了「任期内让人印象深刻的歌曲」的歌单。事实上，奥巴马从 2015 年起就开始和公众分享其歌单。</p>
<p>大家在国内的音乐应用上也能搜到据此制作的歌单。</p>